#

Tomato and Cucumber Salad

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing salad that combines juicy tomatoes and crisp cucumbers, perfect for a light meal or side dish.

Ingredients

  • tomatoes: 2 large, sliced
  • cucumbers: 1 large, sliced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh basil (optional): a few leaves, torn
